data.description: Experience timeless elegance in this charming home with distinctive character. Boasting 3 beds, 2 full baths, and 2 half baths, the master bedroom on the first level offers a serene retreat. Revel in the architectural beauty of high vaulted ceilings and a second floor loft. the first floor's versatile multi-purpose rooms are connected to a spacious living space.  Indulge in the outdoor oasis featuring a kitchen, a relaxing hot tub, seating area, and a porch overlooking a tranquil pond.
